Package: RegCompassR
Title: Simplified Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity Potential Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Provides a Layer 1 workflow for annotated Seurat v4 RNA+ATAC multiome objects and a RegCompassR 1.0 Layer 2 workflow centered on selected-subnetwork, multiome/GPR-weighted, COMPASS-like two-step penalty linear programming. Layer 2 reports reaction capacity support scores, penalties, feasibility flags, solver status, and internal vmax diagnostics rather than true fluxes or enzyme activity.
